{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_01","textHome":"あたしの名前は南津 涼子！神浜近郊に住む@、時女一族の末裔だ！つっても、自分が時@女って知ったのは最近なんだけどな！まあ@期間は関係ねぇ。あたしが時女で、その時@女が日の本の為に戦うってんなら、協力し@ない手はねえよな！さあ、待ってろよ、神@浜!!"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305800}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_17","textHome":"両親があたしに残したのはこの体と魂だけだ\nった。体を失った今、己の魂のままに生き\nることが、両親の生きた証になるんだと思\nう。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":0}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_18","textHome":"あたしゃ嘘が苦手だ。特に自分につく嘘が一@番苦手だ。ということですまん！ろくな理@由も方便もねェけど、あたしは全力でお節@介を焼く！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_19","textHome":"これはいわゆる必殺技なのか？なら、技名叫\nぶ練習しねぇとな！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_20","textHome":"これでもっと人が救える。ああ、そのために\n強くなったんだから！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":200}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_21","textHome":"力が悪いんじゃねェ。力を得て傲慢になるか\n穏やかになるか、それは本人の心持ち次第\nだ！あたしは絶対に、力には溺れねぇぞ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":1}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_22","textHome":"不思議だ…。妙に落ち着いてる。力を得るっ\nてのは…、悟るってのは…、こういうこと\nなんだな。ただ漠然と魔女と戦ってた頃は\n、こんな風になンなかった。時女のみんな\nにあたしも影響受けてンだな"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305800}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_23","textHome":"この世はすっかり奈落のようになっちまった\nのかもしれない。でも、全て人間が起こし\nたことだから、人間が解決できる。あたし\nは諦めない。ここで倒れたら、とーちゃん\nかーちゃんに合わせる顔がねェ"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":1}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_24","textHome":"おう、待ちくたびれたぞ！お前さんのこと考\nえながら座禅してたから、警策で叩かれま\nくったんだぞ！お前さんは煩悩じゃねェよ\nな！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_25","textHome":"おはようさん！ずいぶん早起きじゃねえか！\nあたしは今、寺の掃除が終わったところだ\n。掃除も作務って言って、立派な修行なん\nだぞ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_26","textHome":"腹減った！メシ―！いただきます！ごちそう\nさま！…ちょっとはしたなかったか…？た\nはは、恥ずかしいねェ。でも…ガマンでき\nねェんだ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"id":305800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_02","textHome":"あたしは南津 涼子！寺育ちの魔法少女だ！@毎日修行して、心身を鍛えてる！…は？い@やカツラじゃねぇよ。地毛だよ。僧侶じゃ@ねェよ"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_27","textHome":"この時間、住職はお通夜に出かけてあたしは@留守番なんだ。じーちゃんの浄安寺でも今@の水徳寺でも同じ。…なんか命について考@えちまうな"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":300}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_28","textHome":"今日も終わりだな！全力で生き抜いた、楽し\nい１日だったぞ！明日はもっと楽しく生き\nるために、今から全力で…寝るぞーーーー\n!!"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":200}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_29","textHome":"なーっはっは！観念しろ！この学校の風紀を\n乱す奴ァ、あたしが成敗してやる！…は？\nあたしは風紀委員じゃねェぞ？これはただ\nの独善だ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_30","textHome":"魔女のあの禍々しさ、どれだけの穢れを抱え\nたらあんなンになっちまうんだろうな。…\n待ってろ！今、楽にしてやる！…魔女だっ\nて救うんだ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_31","textHome":"あたしそっくりだなー。仏教には「自己に克\nつ者こそ最上の勝利者」なんて言葉がある\nが…。いや、これはそういうことじゃねぇ\nな"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.8,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_32","textHome":"うひゃー。すげー数の魔法少女だな。…みん@な可愛らしい格好だから…なんか拝みたく@なってくるな。三十三間堂に来た気分だ"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_33","textHome":"あたしは小さい頃に両親が死んでよ、それで\nじーちゃんの浄安寺に引き取られたんだ。\nこんなあたしでも最初は泣いてばっかだっ\nたらしいな"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_34","textHome":"泣いてばっかだったあたしだけど、じーちゃ\nんの説法とか厳しすぎる修行のせいで泣い\nてる暇がなくなったんだ。…感謝しねぇと\nな"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":305800,"motion":300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_35","textHome":"今、世話になってるのは参京区の水徳寺って@寺だ。時女一族なんだってな。あの爺さん@も…魔法少女になれたりするのか…？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":400}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_36","textHome":"マギアユニオンもプロミストブラッドも、み\nんな信念があって衝突してるってのはわか\nってる。でも、話し合いで解決する希望は\n捨てたくねぇ"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_03","textHome":"暴走した正義ほど、悪いもんはねェんだよ"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":305800}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_37","textHome":"ちはるは本当に名探偵だよ。テレビが全然点\nかなくて困ってたら、あたしが持ってンの\nはエアコンのリモコンだって気づいたんだ\n。すげぇよ"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":200}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_38","textHome":"すなお？あいつはそんな怖い奴じゃねぇぞ。\n辛い選択を迫られて生きてきたが、根はと\nっても優しい普通の子だ。…お菓子も好き\nだし。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_39","textHome":"静香はおもしれ―奴だよな。…でもよ、それ\nで侮っちゃあいけねぇよ。アイツはやる奴\nだ。何を？そんなのは知らねェ。でもやる\nんだ。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":200}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_40","textHome":"どうして悪ってのはどこに行っても、どれだ\nけ時間が経っても消えないんだろうな。…\nそれならいっそ、あたしは阿修羅になって\n…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":305800}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_41","textHome":"お前さん、意外といい体してんなー。触って\nいいか？…では。うん…。うん。ああ…。\nおほっ。…。触りすぎたな。ありがとうご\nざいます。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":305800,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_42","textHome":"矯正しがいのある奴だ"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_43","textHome":"寺生まれ、ナメんなよ"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_44","textHome":"喝!!"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_45","textHome":"安心しろ、あたしは死なねえから"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_46","textHome":"強くなって出直してこい！"}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_04","textHome":"ここ…なーんかあンだよなぁ"}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_05","textHome":"よし、何もかも完全に解決したな！"}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_012.exp.json","id":305800,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3058_00_13","textHome":"修行の成果だ！今日は肉食うぞ！肉！え、ま@た修行…？"}]},{"au